{"tid":999623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鴨寮街貓貓墮樓 跌落排檔頂部亡","createTime":"2019-01-29T00:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T00:27:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f7df331d337f4eb2916c3564218580ed594c393","tid":999623,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T00:19:10.000Z","msg":"深水埗鴨寮街203號對開，凌晨5時許，一隻花貓從大廈高處墮下，趺落路邊一個攤販排檔的頂部，發出一聲巨響，街坊見狀報警。消防員到場協助爬上排檔頂部，惟花貓已氣絕身亡，現場亦發現一隻玩具龜，於是撿起一併放入膠袋，轉交警員帶走，待愛護協助人員稍後取走檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190129/59197132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197132&d=AMPtd42ADahZ7WU%2BVKQ9taWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=dbafaaf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197132&h=b1644990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190129/59197132</a>"},{"pid":"c1e94863d8badbb62248c560d39d672a8f818fdf","tid":999623,"uid":232466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貪玩呀貓貓"},{"pid":"decb335dc00dcd473bb5fb96dd473f0a0206aabd","tid":999623,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"貓貓唔知咁高架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}